failures.explanation:
The DatabricksNotebook activity "nb_WriteRunID" contains an incorrect baseParameters configuration. The source stage "WriteRunID" expects parameter "EntryName" to be passed using the SpecialCase rule for Stage-scoped variables with an appended literal (Initial.JobName:"RunID"). According to the rule, the correct expression must be:
{"value": "@concat(variables('JobName'),':RunID')", "type": "Expression"}

Actual configuration found:
"WriteRunID_a1": {"value": "@concat(variables('JobName'),'RunID')", "type": "Expression"}

The colon separator is missing, causing an incorrect value to be supplied to the child routine. No other parameters in this activity require changes, but this single mis-configured parameter violates the mandatory parameter-passing guidelines.

